# User changelog #

### v0.6.1

* Remove unneeded operations causing failure in some cases.

### v0.6.0-rc0

* Added the "multiple" option to shots.
* Changed the API to start a sequence from the device.
    * the global sequence controller no longer defines how to retrieve the controller of sequences started by the device
    * the dispatcher takes an additional parameter when starting a sequence: the controller instance
* Added the "out_of_sequence_callback" callback.
* Bug fixes & some code refactoring.
* Removed the "user_callback_directory" configuration option for the server.

### v0.5.0-rc1

* First usable release

